{{Unreferenced|date = August 2015}}The '''Bratislava International School of Liberal Arts''' ('''BISLA'''), located in the [[Old Town, Bratislava|Old Town]] of [[Bratislava]], [[Slovakia]], is the first [[liberal arts college]] in [[Central Europe]]. A private, accredited three-year degree-granting undergraduate institution, it opened in September 2006.

